column3:
CONSENT FORM
I have been informed about the procedures of the study. I have understood the procedures of the study. I have understood that I have the right to refuse my consent or withdraw at any time during the study. I am aware that participating in this study requires me to give time for filling this questionnaire and there are no tangible or monetary benefits of participation.

NUMBER OF MINUTES
